    This is a block comment.
    Just like GO
*/

// Also supplied by the scanner used by GO.

# Hash comments are custom.

A->B: This is a /* tricky */ remark.
B->A: This is the response // of the remark.
A->B: Hash comments #are not supported# in remarks.

# B->A: This is missing

  B->A: Bla
  A->B: Bla
*/

                end
            end
        end
    end
end

        Proxy->Client: Error
    end
end
